<hr>

<!-- Introduction -->

<p style="text-align:center; font-style:italic; color:black;">
Amrita Vishwa Vidyapeetham is a leading multidisciplinary research university in India.
It was founded by <b>Mata Amritanandamayi Devi (Amma)</b> and is headquartered in
Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu. The university is accredited with an <b>'A++'</b> grade by NAAC
and is recognized by the University Grants Commission (UGC).
</p>

<p style="text-align:center;">
<b>Founder:</b> Mata Amritanandamayi Devi <br>
<b>Established:</b> 2003 <br>
<b>Headquarters:</b> Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India
</p>

